snippet.title: One Drop in game Video
snippet.description:
This video is an in-game play video from One Drop, and although there are still some unfinished parts, the basic play remains unchanged.

The official release is on January 26th, and you can search for "One drop" on Steam or add it to the steam list through the link, so please pay a lot of attention.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2755670/One_Drop/
